{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"9":"The Chapters on Marriage"},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1845,"hadithnumber_last":2015,"arabicnumber_first":1845,"arabicnumber_last":2015}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1978,"arabicnumber":1978,"text":"حدثنا ابو كريب، حدثنا ابو خالد، عن الاعمش، عن شقيق، عن مسروق، عن عبد الله بن عمرو، قال قال رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم \" خياركم خياركم لنسايهم","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":134}}]}